issue.title: Splash screen image and drug record buttons
Splash screen image and drug record buttons
Splash screen image and drug record buttons
UI Improvements
issue.body:
Iterate on the current design of the app to make it simple, clean, and easy to navigate.

The design should optimize accessibility of the app.

Pharmacists/Clinicians [nekoTap professional]:
- busy pharmacists with <2 minutes to spare on this device
- hospital pharmacists/nurses giving discharge instructions to the patient

Users [nekoTap]:
- elderly
- young children (8 y.o)
- babysitters using this app for the first time
- patients with difficulty seeing (including colorblindness)
